ocation is accessible through any computer or mobile device from any spot in the world. With unique Revolutionary GPS\/GSM\/Wi-Fi\/BT Hybrid tracking, Tracki use 4 different technologies to accurately Locate anything Worldwide. GPS utilizing Global Positioning Satellite technology to locate outdoor within 30-150 feet (10-50 meters) accuracy. Wi-Fi is used for indoor tracking and Bluetooth for the last 10-60 feet (3-20 meters) and as far as 20,000 miles .<\/p><p>Tracki GPS Tracker is including SIM card requires no long contracts. Device is working out of the box easy to use, up and running within minutes.<\/p>","text_size":"typeset","secondary_color":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker","highlight_color":"#ffb503","button_label":"Shop Now","button_size":"medium","button_link":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tracki-2021-model-mini-real-time-gps-tracker-788444.jpg","media_background_color":"#000000"}},"slide_tyQt6f":{"type":"slide","settings":{"title":"How does it work?","heading_size":"h1","description":"<p>Simply attach your Tracki to the person or thing you wish to locate and see their location information from the website or mobile app. GPS and cellular technology sends the location information to Tracki's servers where you can access the information from anywhere<strong>Secured<\/strong>and in<strong>Real-Time<\/strong><\/p>","text_size":"typeset","secondary_color":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker","highlight_color":"#ffb503","button_label":"Shop Now","button_size":"medium","button_link":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tracki-2021-model-mini-real-time-gps-tracker-993867.jpg","media_background_color":"#000000"}},"slide_CeWeCt":{"type":"slide","settings":{"title":"Tracki allows you to:","heading_size":"h1","description":"<ul><li>Track down the whereabouts & driving path of vehicles, boats, planes<\/li><li>Track your assets and valuables<\/li><li>Track your drone flight path and find it if it gets lost<\/li><li>Manage and track fleet, boats and employees activity<\/li><li>Track stolen motorcycle, bicycle, construction equipment etc.<\/li><li>Locate your children, pets, or elderly relatives at any given time<\/li><li>Know when your child has exited a set safety zone<\/li><li>Find a lost family member with Dementia or Alzheimer’s Disease<\/li><li>Follow up on lost luggage or a business shipment<\/li><li>Aid your loved ones in distress<\/li><\/ul>","text_size":"typeset","secondary_color":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker","highlight_color":"#ffb503","button_label":"Shop Now","button_size":"medium","button_link":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tracki-2021-model-mini-real-time-gps-tracker-735898.jpg","media_background_color":"#000000"}}},"block_order":["slide_pBjTdT","slide_tyQt6f","slide_CeWeCt"],"name":"t:sections.dual-scroll.presets.name","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"h1","heading_tag":"h2","heading_alignment":"center","enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker","narrow":true,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36,"heading_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#ffffff","description_color":"#b2b2b2","panel_background_color":"#272c32","border_color":"#2f353c","button_background_color":"#000000","button_text_color":"#ffffff","highlight_color":"#ffb503","transition_type":"scroll","media_rotation":0,"media_scale":80,"enable_media_shadow":true}},"16448509603d973c1e":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"16448509602c39a70e-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"OUR FIRST <em>FLAGSHIP<\/em>","heading_size":"h1","heading_tag":"h2","enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"solid-color"}},"16448509602c39a70e-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>\"Dynasty Headphone are beautifully made headphones, offering a <em>level of luxury<\/em> that we’ve come to expect from the Danish audio brand. Their expansive sound and good noise cancellation are augmented by an excellent control app.\"<\/p>","text_size":"typeset2","secondary_color":false,"enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"marker"}}},"block_order":["16448509602c39a70e-0","16448509602c39a70e-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"text_alignment":"left","mobile_text_alignment":"left","horizontal_content":false,"narrow":true,"show_divider":false,"use_custom_colors":false,"colors_button_label":"#ffffff","colors_button_background":"#1a1b18","colors_text":"#212326","colors_background":"#ffffff","colors_highlight":"#aa723e","gradient_background":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"product-details":{"type":"product-details","blocks":{"product-details-0":{"type":"description","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":""}},"product-details-1":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Specifications","content":"<ul><li>Smallest & lightest - (1.75x1.5x0.55) inches<\/li><li>Not only for the US & Canada, but a worldwide coverage - up to 190 countries<\/li><li>Additional indoor tracking using WiFi & Bluetooth<\/li><li>The lowest monthly subscription you can find - as low as $9.95\/mo<\/li><li>Optional extra 3,500mAh magnetic battery<\/li><li>Replaceable battery<\/li><li>SOS panic button + 2 extra alert buttons<\/li><li>5 years of history<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"product-details-2":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Battery Life","content":"<ul><li>1-month battery life in battery save mode<\/li><li>6-months battery life in save mode with an optional extra battery<\/li><li>2-3 days battery life tracking 1-5 times\/min<\/li><li>3-months battery life tracking once a day<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"product-details-3":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"What’s included","content":"<ul><li>Belt clip<\/li><li>Magnet<\/li><li>Lanyard<\/li><li>Keychain for attachment<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"60eeb066-dd65-49d7-b86e-8ef785719e6b":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Warranty information","content":"<p>Full lifetime warranty: free replacement of all lost or damaged products purchased with a warranty.<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["produ